{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idab831024-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s9625"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9625"},"text":"§ 9625.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Ordnance property: officers of the armed forces; civilian employees of the Department of the Air Force; American National Red Cross; educational institutions; homes for veterans’ orphans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idab831025-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s9625/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary of the Air Force may sell articles of ordnance property to officers of other armed forces for their use in the service, in the same manner as these articles are sold to officers of the Air Force or the Space Force.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idab831026-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s9625/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Under such regulations as the Secretary may prescribe, ordnance stores may be sold to civilian employees of the Department of the Air Force and to the American National Red Cross.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idab831027-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s9625/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Articles of ordnance property may be sold to educational institutions and to State soldiers’ and sailors’ orphans’ homes for maintaining the ordnance and ordnance stores issued to those institutions and homes.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"